{"tid":2349181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文在寅任期最後1年　南韓執政黨黨魁：將提議特赦李明博、朴槿惠","createTime":"2021-01-01T10:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T11:21:45.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fafe7060d9731f20a8fa7598c7a2d3aab6ac0e15","tid":2349181,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:57:48.000Z","msg":"李洛淵說，今年是文在寅任期的最後一年，有必要在適當的時候解決這個問題，以緩解社會矛盾，實現國民團結。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，李洛淵的言論可能代表文在寅政府將在任期內就此做出決策，由於兩位前總統當前所處法律狀態不同，可能對已被判刑的李明博實施特赦，並對仍在受審階段的朴槿惠解除刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n報導指，李洛淵在接受採訪前已與文在寅進行了單獨面談，就政局等問題進行了全面討論。<br />\n<br />\n為慶祝新年，文在寅政府日前展開任內第4次特赦，人數為3024人，但政治犯排除在外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210101/36Q4GIZRABCSVOMCSAFFDLAEMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210101%2F36Q4GIZRABCSVOMCSAFFDLAEMU%2F&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=8ce74e52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210101%2F36Q4GIZRABCSVOMCSAFFDLAEMU%2F&h=dd720b06\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210101/36Q4GIZRABCSVOMCSAFFDLAEMU/</a>"},{"pid":"b3df9e715515cf045fc4705556a6c23fd41a3d52","tid":2349181,"uid":40267,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:12:33.000Z","msg":"李明博就話<br />\n朴害死咁多人都特赦唔驚暴動咩"},{"pid":"9a88e9d1f3c19dbbebd3fdef0d35f11b5b3bb29b","tid":2349181,"uid":27251,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:13:59.000Z","msg":"朴殺左班學生，坐一世都唔夠"},{"pid":"cd7f1be425c554bc19143774120f8b71dba4d714","tid":2349181,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"文在寅而家鋪定後路<br />\n<br />\n等下任總統特赦自己"},{"pid":"731ece521987306206b6ef2ac8ba3bec1a05e647","tid":2349181,"uid":66378,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"世越號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo